{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": "We need to create a custom MachineConfigPool for our GPU-enabled nodes (labeled with node-role.kubernetes.io/gpu-worker) along with a KubeletConfig that sets a custom systemReserved memory of 2Gi and cpuManagerPolicy to 'static' specifically for that pool. Please create both YAML resources following the project's documented best practices and constraints, ensuring the pool correctly inherits from the worker pool."}, "timestamp": "2026-06-22T21:38:18.497Z"}
